assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢得黎 自欺欺人又咁勁  唉  想叫你理性d  ,但我知當局者迷,徒然<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以你話我點敢同現實朋友呻...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}